longBusinessSummary: Harbor Bankshares Corporation operates as the holding company for The Harbor Bank of Maryland that provides various banking services. The company offers checking accounts, savings accounts, and investment accounts; cards; individual retirement plans; certificate of deposits; mortgages; personal loans and line of credit; bill pay services; and online and mobile banking services. It also offers business loans; remote deposit, cash management, and merchant services. The company operates through seven branches and primarily serves the Baltimore, Maryland metropolitan area. Harbor Bankshares Corporation was founded in 1982 and is based in Baltimore, Maryland.
